---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NewsletterSignup from '../../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro';
import Comments from '../../../components/Comments.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="MOPS Morning - Stephanie McGennis"
  description="The excitement and hope in my heart as I prepared for my first MOPS meeting of the Fall."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-32 px-4 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <a href="/blog/alattetodomama" class="inline-flex items-center text-mcgennis-maroon hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
          </svg>
          Back to A Latte to Do Mama
        </a>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        MOPS Morning
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400">by Stephanie Kay McGennis</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">September 12, 2023</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social Sharing -->
  <section class="py-8 px-4 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://themcgennisfamily.com/blog/alattetodomama/mops-morning" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-mcgennis-navy hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white rounded-lg transition-all text-xs font-medium shadow-sm hover:shadow-md" aria-label="Share on Facebook">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">Share</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://themcgennisfamily.com/blog/alattetodomama/mops-morning&text=MOPS%20Morning" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-mcgennis-maroon hover:bg-opacity-90 text-white rounded-lg transition-all text-xs font-medium shadow-sm hover:shadow-md" aria-label="Share on Twitter">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M23.953 4.57a10 10 0 01-2.825.775 4.958 4.958 0 002.163-2.723c-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184a4.92 4.92 0 00-8.384 4.482C7.69 8.095 4.067 6.13 1.64 3.162a4.822 4.822 0 00-.666 2.475c0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096a4.904 4.904 0 01-2.228-.616v.06a4.923 4.923 0 003.946 4.827 4.996 4.996 0 01-2.212.085 4.936 4.936 0 004.604 3.417 9.867 9.867 0 01-6.102 2.105c-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067a13.995 13.995 0 007.557 2.209c9.053 0 13.998-7.496 13.998-13.985 0-.21 0-.42-.015-.63A9.935 9.935 0 0024 4.59z"/>
            </svg>
            Tweet
          </a>
          <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(window.location.href); alert('Link copied to clipboard!');" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white rounded-lg transition-all text-xs font-medium shadow-sm hover:shadow-md" aria-label="Copy link">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 16H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 12h8a2 2 0 002-2v-8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-8a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">Copy</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">
            The excitement and hope in my heart as I prepared for my first MOPS meeting of the Fall.
          </p>

          <!-- MOPS Prep Image -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <img src="/images/blog/mops-prep.png" alt="MOPS morning preparation - diaper bag with supplies" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md" />
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center mt-2 italic">Getting ready for MOPS - the little package I prepared last minute</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I'm blessed to stay home with my baby. It's just he and I right now. He turned 1 almost a month ago. This is the cute little package I got ready for him last night (v. last minute unsurprisingly) to take to MOPS with us this morning like the instructions said on Facebook.
            </p>

            <p>
              MOPS = moms of preschoolers or something like that if you don't know or don't have a group in your area. If you do have a group in your area, check it out! (Learn more at <a href="https://www.mops.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-mcgennis-maroon hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors underline">MOPS International</a>.)
            </p>

            <p>
              I can't begin to tell you the excitement and hope in my heart and mind as I prepared this tiny bag so I could bring my backpack purse with me that also houses diaper supplies. I was a little sad that he's not a tiny baby who would be staying with me, but excited for freedom and enjoying some enrichment time without someone hanging on me. If you're navigating the chaos of <a href="/blog/alattetodomama/a-latte-to-do" class="text-mcgennis-maroon hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors underline">busy parenting routines</a>, you know exactly what I mean.
            </p>

            <p>
              MOPS was scary when I first tried it last Spring and I'd be lying if I wasn't a little nervous to go this morning, but I mainly had joy in my heart as I prepared. If you're looking for encouragement about finding your community and support system as a mom, read about <a href="/blog/alattetodomama/coffee-shop-prayers" class="text-mcgennis-maroon hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors underline">how I find moments with God in everyday chaos</a>.
            </p>

            <p>
              My excitement only bubbled over when I walked inside and saw familiar faces, an iced coffee station, breakfast pizza, and the cutest decorations. I put on a name tag and walked to drop my 13mo baby off in the nursery.
            </p>

            <p>
              We weren't necessary running early but pretty well on time so when I got to the door of the nursery, I was met by the screams and cries of...
            </p>

            <p class="italic text-gray-500">
              [To be continued...]
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comments Section -->
  <Comments />

  <!-- Related Posts -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">More from A Latte to Do Mama</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/blog/alattetodomama/fall-allergies-and-prayer" class="group bg-white rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-mcgennis-maroon overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/blog/leo-yard.png"
              alt="Fall Allergies and Prayer"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight group-hover:text-mcgennis-maroon transition-colors mb-2">
              Fall Allergies and Prayer
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3 font-light">
              The literal bane of my existence when I'm trying to live my best pumpkin spice life.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">October 6, 2023</span>
              <div class="flex items-center text-mcgennis-maroon font-medium group-hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors text-sm">
                Read More →
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/alattetodomama/a-latte-to-do" class="group bg-white rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 hover:border-mcgennis-maroon overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/blog/a-latte-to-do-notepad.png"
              alt="A Latte to Do - Introduction"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight group-hover:text-mcgennis-maroon transition-colors mb-2">
              A Latte to Do - Introduction
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3 font-light">
              Do people still blog? If they do, do other people still read it? I guess we'll see.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">September 5, 2023</span>
              <div class="flex items-center text-mcgennis-maroon font-medium group-hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition-colors text-sm">
                Read More →
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Back to Blog List -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <a href="/blog/alattetodomama" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-medium tracking-wide hover:border-mcgennis-maroon hover:text-mcgennis-maroon transition-all duration-300">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to All Posts
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
